parameters:
Zerachiel: Oh, they've already noticed
us.
Priest Soldier A: It is as the Holy Maiden has foretold. We have no choice but to follow the divine oracle.

Priest Soldier B: Understood, we will
capture them. We will hand them over to
the Holy Maiden.

Zerachiel: It seems like you intend to
fight me.

Zerachiel: You will regret aiming your
weapon at the strongest angel like me.

Priest Soldier B: We might not
stand a chance...

Priest Soldier A: There's no other
choice, let's retreat. We'll report to
the Holy Maiden.
Zerachiel: Looks like they ran away.

Zerachiel: It's troublesome if
they call allies, so let's quickly proceed
further into the depths.
